{{ja-kanjitab|おと|yomi=k}}
{{IPAfont|⟨oto<sub>2</sub>⟩}} → *{{IPAchar|/otə/}} → {{IPAchar|/oto/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=おと|-}}.

Ultimately from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*ətə}}.

{{ja-noun|おと}}

# a [[sound]]
#: {{ja-usex|'''音'''を[[漏らす]]|'''おと''' を もらす|to let out a '''sound'''}}
# when used with a "hear" verb, a [[rumor]] or [[fame]] {{rfv-sense|ja}}
# [[news]], [[tiding]]s
# a [[reply]], [[response]]

{{ja-kanjitab|と|yomi=k}}
{{IPAfont|⟨to<sub>2</sub>⟩}} → *{{IPAchar|/tə/}} → {{IPAchar|/to/}}

Shift from ''oto'' above, with the initial ''o'' being dropped.

The drop is likely due to [[haplology]] with the possessive particle {{ja-r|の}}.

{{ja-noun|と}}

# [[sound]]; [[echo]]; [[voice]]
#* {{RQ:Manyoshu|14|3453}}, text [http://jti.lib.virginia.edu/japanese/manyoshu/Man14Yo.html#3453 here]
#*: {{ja-usex|m=可是能'''等'''能 登抱吉和伎母賀 吉西斯伎奴 多母登乃久太利 麻欲比伎尓家利|m_kana=かぜの'''と'''の とほきわぎもが きせしきぬ たもとのくだり まよひきにけり|風の'''音'''の遠き我妹が着せし衣%[[袂|手%本]]のくだりまよひ来にけり|かぜ の '''と''' の とほき わぎも が きせし-きぬ% た%もとのくだり まよひきにけり|rom=kaze no '''to''' no tōki wagimo ga kiseshi-kinu tamoto no kudari, mayoi-ki ni keri|My dear wife, far away (as the '''sound''' of the wind), some threads of the sleeves of the kimono you made me wear have come to be worn and chafed!<ref>{{cite-book|1964|Jan Lodewijk Pierson, Jr.|The Makura-Kotoba of the Manyôśû|location=Leiden|publisher=Brill Archive|page=54}}</ref>|sort=と}}

